## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the rapidly evolving nature of the COVID-19 pandemic and related conspiracy theories. Additionally, the psychological and social factors contributing to these beliefs are complex and multifaceted, making it challenging to provide a comprehensive analysis within the scope of this report. Further research is needed to explore these dynamics in greater depth.